Package: pivotR
Title: RStudio Plugin For Visual Data Investigation
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Neil", "Charles", , "neil.d.charles@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Interactive charting of an R data frame via an RStudio Addin. The addin is able to draw various types of charts and aggregates data on the fly to speed up investigation of a dataset.
